      "instruction": "<p><strong>Boil</strong> a kettle</p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong> and chop the potatoes into large chunks</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> them to a pot of salted boiling water over a high heat and cook for 15 min or until&nbsp;fork-tender</p>",
