          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, strip the thyme leaves from the stalks and chop them finely</p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong>&nbsp;and finely chop the onion<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Chop</strong> the tomatoes into a large dice</p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong> and finely chop (or grate) the garlic</p>",
      "order": 2,
