    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Return </strong>the pan to a medium-low heat and add the onion and garlic</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook</strong> for 3 min or until the onion is soft but not coloured</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the chilli flakes (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
