      "instruction": "<p><strong>Return</strong> the sausages to the pan</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the tomatoes and 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">(400ml)</span> water</p>\r\n<p><strong>Crumble</strong>&nbsp;in the stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> and stir to dissolve</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook</strong>&nbsp;for 10-15 min or until the sausages are cooked through and a thick sauce remains</p>",
